===Arena Football League===
Bright then entered the [[Arena Football League]] (AFL) and over the course of a year and a half, he played for the [[Philadelphia Soul]], [[New Orleans VooDoo]] and the [[Pittsburgh Power]] before signing with the [[Wichita Wild]] midway through the 2012 season. Playing in all seven of the Wild<U+2019>s remaining games last season, Bright tallied 33 total tackles, one and a half sacks and two forced fumbles.

